In , the same field had
scalar curl
Q_x-P_y=1-(-1)=2.
So curl and divergence measure different behavior:

  \begin{array}{c|c}
  \text{curl} \amp \text{tendency to circulate}\\[1mm]
  \text{divergence} \amp \text{tendency to flow outward}
  \end{array}
